{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151010/extras/Gameplay.gif?t=1729055494\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">---------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Game/Demo is still being actively developed and updated 2-3 times each week. Please follow progress and leave feedback through our discord or Steam Discussions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">---------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Soul Kira is a multiplayer 2D Platform Shooter game, taking gameplay elements from Shoot 'em Up, Dungeon Crawler and Roguelike. Soul Kira currently supports upto 16 players in a match, with plans to scale upto 100 players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game Modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-PvP Mode: Free for All, fight against other players in solo battles or as a team</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-PvE Mode: Fight monsters and other entities in the Soul Kira universe, clear dungeons and levels like a retro arcade game and unlock rewards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-PvPvE Mode: Total chaos ensues when players will have to fight other players and also monsters in a free for all. Beware of other Monarch Bosses also taking part in battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Planned Modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Battle Royale: Huge inter-dimensional map(s), 100 players, lets do some soul hunting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All above modes can be played solo or as a team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weapons:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Pistol <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151010/extras/pistol.gif?t=1729055494\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Rifle <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151010/extras/rifle.gif?t=1729055494\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Machine Gun <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151010/extras/machinegun.gif?t=1729055494\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> SMG <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151010/extras/smg.gif?t=1729055494\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Shotgun <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151010/extras/shotgun.gif?t=1729055494\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Sniper <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151010/extras/sniper.gif?t=1729055494\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Bazooka <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151010/extras/bazooka.gif?t=1729055494\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Flamethrower<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151010/extras/flamethrower.gif?t=1729055494\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Grenade <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151010/extras/grenade.gif?t=1729055494\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Frag Grenade <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151010/extras/frag.gif?t=1729055494\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Toxic Grenade <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151010/extras/toxic.gif?t=1729055494\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">----------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Character Creator System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Character Creator System allows each pla